messages.message: Upon deletion of a project, am not seeing a Toast notification to indicate the project was successfully deleted
Is the project still disappearing? You should see that in AI Hub we do not use success toasts anywhere.

Ah it is disappearing, my use case might be unique since I have a ton of projects with UUID's so there's a little more friction to confirm that a project was deleted. For the typical user this seems like a nonissue.
